How does team sign-up work? Will it automatically sign up everyone in the team? Or will I be able to choose who in the team for sign up? (Not everyone is available at the same time)
It will **__only__** the whole team. If the team as a whole is not eligible for an offer, it will not sign up the team
If someone is AFK or not available, you have to kick them from the group and invite them again later
